BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE OF THE ONE HUNDRED FOURTEENTH
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, THE HOUSE OF
REPRESENTATIVES CONCURRING, that we honor and recognize the Bachman-McCoy Farm
on the occasion of the property being placed in the National Register of Historic Places and
commemorate the many accomplishments and contributions of the Bachman-McCoy family.
